[LayoutBox, BracedBox, layoutNested, layoutCurrent, layoutPlus, bracedNested, bracedCurrent, bracedPlus, ordinary](extension-receiver-scope-lib.ssc)

# Imported receiver ownership

```scalascript
val layout = LayoutBox(2)
println(layout.layoutNested)
println(layout.layoutCurrent)
println(layout.layoutPlus(3))

val braced = BracedBox(3)
println(braced.bracedNested)
println(braced.bracedCurrent)
println(braced.bracedPlus(4))
println(ordinary(8))
```
